§7Competition for resources leads to destruction and then to reorganization and rebirth...
The Machine has three parameters: Digger Temperature, Limiting Temperature and Excavator Range
Consume 1B Drilling Fluid per second to output 512 * Excavator Range random raw ores from the current planet
Digger Temperature increase with the Excavator Range increase, when it greater than or equal to Limiting Temperature the machine will be interrupted
Initial Limiting Temperature is §c3500K§r and the value is N when putting different kinds of drill head in controller
N = 3500 + Current Limiting Temperature - (Limiting Temperature / 10) * (Excavator Range / 10)
Extra raw ores produced when Digger Temperature <= Limiting Temperature / 5 and >= Limiting Temperature / 7
Consume different coolant(PCB Coolant、Super Coolant、Gelid Cryotheum) to decrease Digger Temperature
Available Drill Head: Titanium, Stainless Steel, Tungsten Steel, HSS-E, Naquadah Alloy, Neutronium

mbe.multiblock.dyson_sphere_deployment_b: Constantly generate energy by launching solar sails

The maximum number of solar sails allowed to be launched is limited by the amount of solar sail nodes
Each launch of the solar sail carrier rocket can increase the number of solar sail nodes by 1, and the maximum number of nodes is 256, each node number can load 100 solar sails
Dyson sphere deployment base station begins to output energy when solar sails >= 100
§7Maximum Energy Output = Amount of Solar Sails / 100§rA §c§lMAX§r
When the number of solar sails is greater than 5000, there will be a (number of solar sails / 2000)% chance of a solar sail damage event every 10 seconds

The number of damaged solar sails recorded after each recycling of ingredient will be reset to 0
